    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm not talking about like, getting drunk or anything. just the single glass of wine i always have. it's not like im taking shots. it feels like a very small amount, so surely the risk isn't *that* high if i just want to make sure the sleeping pill actually works? it seems a bit extreme to say it could be fatal just from one glass.",
